title: Redwood National and State Parks: Photo Gallery
body: Photo Gallery                    Centennial Celebration in the Redwoods!   17 Photos  Photos from our celebration of the NPS centennial. Held near Orick, CA. June 26, 2016.          Wildflowers   18 Photos            Coast Redwoods   32 Photos  Images of coast redwoods (Sequoia sempervirens)            Roosevelt Elk   6 Photos  Images and photos of Roosevelt elk in Redwood National and State Parks.          Birds   17 Photos  Birds found in Redwood National and State Parks          Beaches & Coastline   23 Photos  Views of Redwood's 37 miles of coastline.            Scenics   37 Photos  Scenics views and vistas within and around Redwood National and State Parks.          Fungi   10 Photos  Mushrooms and other fungi.          Tidepools   17 Photos  Plants, animals, and scenery of the tidepools Redwood's 37 miles of coastline.            Slugs and Snails   3 Photos  Banana slugs and other invertebrate slugs and snails.          Rivers and Waterways   1 Photos  Rivers, creeks, streams, and even entire watersheds in Redwood National and State Parks.
